snippet.textDisplay: Piyush Mishra: Pune Concert: A vague date in 2022. I peeped through an opening in the drape  hiding him from the audience before he was to make an appearance that would be equal parts mesmerising & celebrity. In the fashion that could define many a 90s artiste, fascinating & somewhat full of intrigue, he sat there, gracing a bunch of his team with just being present, cigarette in hand, looking mostly at nothing. That sense of being, knowing who he is & what he represents, not only in that moment, but as an eminence carrying the time he became who he became, left me an overwhelmed, quiet & inspired fan. Thank you Piyush. Thank you Ballimaaraan.
